 <div class="text-xs text-muted-text leading-relaxed">{c.why}</div>
 </div>
 ))}
 </div>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">
 Coaching also suits 1s. They're effective mentors when they learn to meet people where they are, not where they think they should be.
 </p>
 </section>

