 <!-- All life paths reference -->
 <section id="all-life-paths" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
 <h2 class="section-h2">All life path numbers at a glance</h2>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-6">
 Understanding how the 1 compares with the other life paths helps put things in context. All nine life paths exist on a spectrum - each one reflects a different set of instincts, strengths, and tensions. Some life paths are more relationship-oriented; others are built for solitude or creative work. Below is a quick look at all nine, plus the three master numbers that sit outside the standard single-digit range.
 </p>

 <div class="lp-grid">
 {[
 { n: 1, label: "The Leader", href: "/learn/life-path-number-1/", active: true },
 { n: 2, label: "The Peacemaker", href: "/learn/life-path-number-2/" },
