 Every life path has strengths and pressure points. The 1 isn't better than the others - just first. Number 9 closes the cycle that 1 opens. Number 5 brings the freedom 1 lacks. Number 3 brings joy. Different numbers, different tools. Understanding your number means finding where you fit in the bigger picture.
 </p>
