 <!-- How to calculate -->
 <section id="calculate" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
 <h2 class="section-h2">How to find your life path number</h2>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
 Your life path number is derived from your birth date by reducing each component (day, month, year) to a single-digit number, then adding those digits together and reducing again. The exception is if any stage produces 11, 22, or 33 - those are master numbers and are not reduced further.
 </p>

 <div class="card-light" style="padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">
 <div style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-body-text);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Example: October 15, 1987</div>
 <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-muted-text);">
 <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Month:</span> October = <strong style="color:var(--color-body-text);margin-left:0.25rem;">10 → 1+0 = 1</strong></div>
 <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Day:</span> 15 → 1+5 = <strong style="color:var(--color-body-text);margin-left:0.25rem;">6</strong></div>
 <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Year:</span> 1987 → 1+9+8+7 = 25 → 2+5 = <strong style="color:var(--color-body-text);margin-left:0.25rem;">7</strong></div>
 <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);padding-top:0.4rem;display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Total:</span> 1+6+7 = 14 → 1+4 = <strong style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);font-size:1rem;margin-left:0.25rem;">5</strong></div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
 To find your life path number, calculate your own date of birth the same way. If the final number reduces to 1, this page is yours. You can also use our free calculator to do it instantly - or read our <a href="/learn/how-to-calculate-life-path-number/" class="text-violet hover:text-soft-gold underline">full guide to calculating your life path number</a> if you want to understand the method properly.
 </p>

 <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:1.5rem;">
 <a href="/learn/life-path-number/#calculator" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:var(--color-violet);color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;padding:0.875rem 1.75rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">
 Calculate your life path number free
 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
 </a>
 </div>
 </section>

